::GoldenEye::

She had a shocked look on her face as Dollen talked to her.  It was 
very apperant that something was bugging him and he wasn't going to 
say anything about it now.  She let go of his hand and transformed 
into eagle mode and flew up. She was about 20 feet in the air and 
stayed at that hieght.  She gave and eagle cry and circled 
Dollen, "When you want to talk, I'll be here."  She then flew slowly 
towards the base were KitKat was gathering the others. She flew so 
she would be just ahead of Dollen, but slow enough that he could keep 
up.
